{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE PREMISE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Imagine coming home after a long and tiring day of work and dreaming of nothing else but sleep... But when you open the door to your bedroom, you find your bed held hostage by horrors beyond your comprehension.<br>Luckily, that probably won't happen to your bed - your task however is to help a guy in this exact predicament. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A fun and scratchy Flash-like artstyle reminiscent of old browser games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some unlockable <span class=\"bb_strike\">drip</span>clothes to freshen your guy up</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Almost 60 rooms full of puzzles that you'll have to get creative with - with a knack for seeking patterns, you might even solve them before lunch!<br>(Let's say, maybe two hours? If you're faster than that, kudos to you - the sleepy guy can't thank you enough ;))</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The puzzles range from as simple as finding a crowbar and breaking into a box, to playing classical music to put an ancient smooze from the void to sleep. Think outside the box!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are secrets hidden behind and under every door, bed and crack.<br>The clock is ticking, the man is tired\u2026 So turn off that lamp and let him sleep!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Completionist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2765910/acc898d4ea12d643d9d0cd88b0b5bec76b3e4e5d.jpg"},{"name":"Frenzy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2765910/3403dd6257701fbbb0995215bde32146aff5c011.jpg"},{"name":"Detective","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2765910/12286